<h2 class="bold font-l">The Commandment of Truth</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Galand is the wielder of the Commandment of Truth; any who lies or breaks any vow in his presence is turned to stone as punishment. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Geas" class='trope-example-link'>Geas</a></p>
